name: Henry Cavill
description:
Henry Cavill TI made from 19 images of our Lord and Savior

  • Download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-web-ui>embeddings folder.
    Then simply add hcavi69 as a part of your prompt and he'll appear, I hope


Will work with all models which were made with 1.5 as a base.

most models and merges are biased towards women and feminine faces so be careful with the prompts.
